name: Twenty-two
description: This chemigram ("writing with chemistry"), which is an experimental camera-less photographic process, is made with basic darkroom supplies (Ilford black and white paper, developer and fixer). The black is from the developer, white from the fixer and gold/brown from a mixture of the two. The purple and pink colour is the undeveloped and unfixed, light exposed paper. The NFT is 8K.
